				There are plenty of Tivo-style solutions out there that do not report this sort of information back to the networks. Even with Tivo I think this is a feature you can choose to opt-out of.
<br />

<br />
If you're renting a PVR from your cable company, on the other hand, you can bet the are tracking you and you won't be able to opt out of it.<br />
